Tanzanian President, John Pombe Magufuli, is dead. His death was confirmed in a state address by Tazania’s Vice-President, Samia Suluhu Hassan. According to her, Magufuli died of a heart condition. “It is with deep regret that I inform you that today on the 17th of March, 2021 at 6 pm we lost our brave leader, the President of the Republic of Tanzania, John Pombe Magufuli.”